08:56.046 --> 09:10.260
but its primary mission is to improve the teaching 
administration, counseling for public schools

09:10.561 --> 09:15.205
of Texas and the nation. We have people majoring in 
things in this college that has no interest in or no

09:16.266 --> 09:22.432
link to public education. I would take a close look 
at that and say if you're in a college of education,

09:23.733 --> 09:40.028
we should be one way or another interested in using 
