09:43.549 --> 09:45.693
everyone in this college is involved one way or 
another. Whether you're an ed psych specialist

09:45.713 --> 09:54.046
who's looking at some specific little element, 
you ought to be looking at how that can improve

09:45.713 --> 09:54.046
public schools and public education. And I would 
not probably be a popular dean by doing that, But to

09:58.874 --> 10:04.521
me, we've got to focus more on our primary mission, 
and that's improving the schools of Texas. And in

10:05.042 --> 10:06.864
doing so, we improve the private schools. We 
improve, we develop professors that can go into

10:08.025 --> 10:16.416
the other universities with the same mindset that 
public schools are the primary thing. Even though

10:16.436 --> 10:28.611
